<p>The SCQM is a four-quadrant framework that evaluates AI writing models across benchmark scores, real-world SEO performance, detection resistance, and cost efficiency. It helps content teams move beyond leaderboard hype and choose models based on outcomes that matter: rankings, traffic, and return on investment.</p>
